General.Name: Everfuel AS
General.Description: Everfuel A/S operates as an integrated green hydrogen fuel company in Norway, Denmark, Sweden, the Netherlands, Germany, and Belgium. The company develops, owns, and operates green hydrogen infrastructure for vertically integrated hydrogen production, distribution, and fueling. It offers hydrogen supply and fueling solutions, as well as for industry stakeholders working with alternative hydrogen-based green fuels and power-to-X-products. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Herning, Denmark. Everfuel A/S is a subsidiary of E.F. Holding ApS.
